---
// MultiAgentTrace.astro — Trace showing multiple agents collaborating
---

<div class="mat-wrap">
  <h3 class="mat-title">Multi-Agent Trace — Watch Them Collaborate</h3>
  <p class="mat-sub">Task: "Write a technical blog post about Kubernetes security"</p>
  <div class="mat-trace">
    <div class="mat-e mat-a1"><div class="mat-t">0ms</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--blue"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--blue">ORCHESTRATOR</div><div class="mat-txt">Breaking task into: research → outline → draft → review. Assigning to specialists.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a2"><div class="mat-t">50ms</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--cyan"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--cyan">RESEARCH AGENT</div><div class="mat-txt">Searching for K8s security best practices, CVE data, RBAC patterns. Found 12 sources.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a3"><div class="mat-t">800ms</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--cyan"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--cyan">RESEARCH AGENT → ORCHESTRATOR</div><div class="mat-txt">Done. Returning 5 key topics with sources: RBAC, Network Policies, Pod Security, Image Scanning, Secrets.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a4"><div class="mat-t">820ms</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--green"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--green">WRITING AGENT</div><div class="mat-txt">Received research. Drafting 5-section blog with intro, examples, and code snippets.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a5"><div class="mat-t">2.1s</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--green"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--green">WRITING AGENT → ORCHESTRATOR</div><div class="mat-txt">Draft complete. 1,200 words. Passing to review.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a6"><div class="mat-t">2.2s</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--amber"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--amber">REVIEW AGENT</div><div class="mat-txt">Checking for accuracy, hallucinations, and missing topics. Found 2 issues: outdated CVE reference, missing network policy example.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a7"><div class="mat-t">3.0s</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--green"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--green">WRITING AGENT</div><div class="mat-txt">Fixing 2 flagged issues. Updated CVE, added NetworkPolicy YAML example.</div></div></div>
    <div class="mat-e mat-a8"><div class="mat-t">3.8s</div><div class="mat-d mat-d--blue"></div><div class="mat-c"><div class="mat-type mat-tp--blue">ORCHESTRATOR</div><div class="mat-txt">All agents done. Final output assembled. Quality score: 94/100.</div></div></div>
  </div>
  <div class="mat-stats"><div class="mat-st"><span class="mat-sv">3.8s</span><span class="mat-sl">Total</span></div><div class="mat-st"><span class="mat-sv">3</span><span class="mat-sl">Agents</span></div><div class="mat-st"><span class="mat-sv">7</span><span class="mat-sl">Handoffs</span></div><div class="mat-st"><span class="mat-sv">$0.04</span><span class="mat-sl">Cost</span></div></div>
</div>

<style>
  .mat-wrap { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f172a, #1e293b); border-radius: 16px; padding: 2rem; margin: 2rem 0; border: 1px solid #334155; }
  .mat-title { color: #f1f5f9; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 700; margin: 0 0 .25rem; }
  .mat-sub { color: #64748b; font-size: .8rem; margin: 0 0 1.5rem; font-family: monospace; }
  .mat-trace { position: relative; padding-left: 16px; }
  .mat-trace::before { content: ''; position: absolute; left: 50px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 1px; background: #334155; }
  .mat-e { display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 8px; opacity: 0; animation: matIn .4s ease-out forwards; }
  .mat-a1{animation-delay:.1s}.mat-a2{animation-delay:.3s}.mat-a3{animation-delay:.5s}.mat-a4{animation-delay:.7s}.mat-a5{animation-delay:.9s}.mat-a6{animation-delay:1.1s}.mat-a7{animation-delay:1.3s}.mat-a8{animation-delay:1.5s}
  .mat-t { color: #475569; font-size: .5rem; font-family: monospace; min-width: 30px; text-align: right; margin-top: 4px; }
  .mat-d { width: 10px; height: 10px; border-radius: 50%; flex-shrink: 0; margin-top: 4px; position: relative; z-index: 1; }
  .mat-d--blue { background: #60a5fa; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(96,165,250,.4); }
  .mat-d--cyan { background: #06b6d4; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(6,182,212,.4); }
  .mat-d--green { background: #4ade80; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(74,222,128,.4); }
  .mat-d--amber { background: #f59e0b; box-shadow: 0 0 6px rgba(245,158,11,.4); }
  .mat-c { flex: 1; padding: 8px 12px; border-radius: 8px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.2); border: 1px solid #334155; }
  .mat-type { font-size: .5rem; font-family: monospace; font-weight: 800; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: .05em; margin-bottom: 3px; }
  .mat-tp--blue { color: #60a5fa; } .mat-tp--cyan { color: #06b6d4; } .mat-tp--green { color: #4ade80; } .mat-tp--amber { color: #f59e0b; }
  .mat-txt { color: #94a3b8; font-size: .7rem; line-height: 1.5; }
  .mat-stats { display: flex; gap: 16px; margin-top: 14px; padding: 12px; background: rgba(0,0,0,.15); border-radius: 10px; border: 1px solid #334155; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .mat-st { text-align: center; } .mat-sv { display: block; color: #e2e8f0; font-size: 1rem; font-weight: 800; font-family: monospace; } .mat-sl { display: block; color: #64748b; font-size: .55rem; font-family: monospace; }
  @keyframes matIn { from { opacity: 0; transform: translateX(-8px); } to { opacity: 1; transform: translateX(0); } }
</style>
